text:
Water Street, south from Fletcher Street. Across the foreground runs Maiden Lane. The gas station at the left runs from Fletcher Street to Maiden Lane. Opened to view there is the warehouse building at the S. E. corner. On the right is another cleared area utilized as another gas station. This extends from Maiden Lane to Pine Street. See View 2 for details of this. Dominating the background is the towering Farmers Trust Bldg.

June 16, 1940
No's. 1-2

P. L. Sperr

VIEW 3

View 3: Water Street, north side from Maiden Lane left to Fletcher Street.

May 8, 1940.
